      "comment": "URANA CYCLONE (1) is yet to break through in 16 starts but has run a number of placings. Was game in defeat when narrowly beaten into second last time. Likely to feature again. PAW AMARLI (8) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (22.92) in a Maiden at Warrnambool latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Can find the frame this time. RAPID WATERBOY (2) jumped from this same draw and was close to the lead throughout before boxing on well and holding a 4 length second (23.24) at this track over 400m in a Rank Limit - Maiden. This tougher but looks a leading chance again. MRS. PUDDLEDUCK (6) found the frame here last start and looks a top-three hope again.",
